  entryId: day_00_prologue
  dayNumber: 0
  title: The Village That Forgets
  bodyText: "I arrived at dusk. They greeted me warmly \u2014 then greeted me again
    an hour later, as if for the first time.\n\nEvery dawn wipes them clean. Names,
    debts, promises. Only the village itself keeps the score: doors I opened stay
    open, paths I cleared stay clear.\n\nIf I want answers, I will have to leave
    marks the morning cannot erase."
  illustration: {fileID: 0}
